headline: Wall Street Lunch: Bitcoin Breaches $111,000 Mark On Historic Pizza Day
summary: Bitcoin (BTC-USD) is setting new highs on the 15th anniversary of the famous crypto pizza transaction that started it all.

headline: 3 Reasons INCY is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Incyte trades at $67 per share and has moved almost in lockstep with the market over the last six months. The stock has lost 6.6% while the S&P 500 is down 2.1%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
